{"tid":927124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗街頭警拔槍 制服持刀男","createTime":"2018-12-04T03:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T05:47:10.000Z","uid":26053,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c0a7a06724d9e1b7a7ceb5efdfe45908bfbe02","tid":927124,"uid":26053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:05:33.000Z","msg":"早上約10時，元朗安樂路有警員拔槍制服疑人。現場消息指，警方接獲多個報案，指有數名戴口罩男子持刀，警員趕至現場，在附近尋獲一名男子持刀站在近馬路的欄杆旁，三名軍裝警員及一名便衣人員，在疑人左右兩旁包圍，其間人員揮動伸縮警棍，喝令他棄刀，更有警員拔槍示警。警方多部衝鋒車趕至現場增援。受事件影響，安樂路馬路一帶暫時封閉。<br />\n<br />\n又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd96ada3ef295a6d650bc2a6431a2e5b6e85444a","tid":927124,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:41:36.000Z","msg":"好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我指普通市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f9d13ab279674348089844eb29306d6ce2e52c","tid":927124,"uid":123848,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"拔槍有咩出奇，開槍都重得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b66ea5bae544b9fa95a4a38d44e952365ca507d","tid":927124,"uid":64379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:49:45.000Z","msg":"有咩問題"},{"pid":"b2833c8dc864e2dba0ea77724754b97d082dc13c","tid":927124,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:51:22.000Z","msg":"有咩問題"},{"pid":"bdc0f54aa0dccec2fd2d39541a914272a9048717","tid":927124,"uid":24044,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9f9d13ab279674348089844eb29306d6ce2e52c","tid":927124,"uid":123848,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"拔槍有咩出奇，開槍都重得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T03